metadata.name: VØID - BEAST SOME MORE
metadata.description:
Get ready to ‘BEAST SOME MORE’! 

The genesis music NFT of VØID has finally landed! This marks the beginning of a new chapter in our lives, the VØID chapter!

What does this mean for you?  
Access to exclusive content, participate in exclusive giveaways, VIP access to the inner circle of the VØID gang, collab requests, and by owning this NFT you get to decide where the VØID project is headed next! Your input and feedback will be valued, and your ideas will be considered for the direction the project takes.

This means that you own a piece of history, but the significance of this music NFT goes far beyond personal benefits. It represents a turning point in the web3 music industry, creating a new era of ownership and collaboration.

  Together, we are rewriting the rules and embracing the limitless possibilities of the web3 music industry.

  Glad to have you on board!
